{"tid":1050677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲四小龍與美日經濟表現分析","createTime":"2019-03-07T04:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T09:51:35.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13f5465dc637b1f9be49a4650334790c13f6b7ac","tid":1050677,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5039093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cw.com.tw%2Farticle%2Farticle.action%3Fid%3D5039093&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QGyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=54d068fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5039093</a><br />\n<br />\n姚明嘉 1986-10-01<br />\n<br />\n今年上半年，在油價、匯率大幅變動下，原本戰力相當的亞洲四小龍，競爭態勢已有顯著改變。與四小龍關係最密切的美日兩大經濟強權，同時各有消長。 <br />\n<br />\n油價下跌及美元眨值、日圓升值，是今年上半年影響國際經濟情勢最大的兩個因素。美國的保護主義高漲，對五個東亞國家（中韓日港星），也都造成了相當程度的困擾。然而不同的國家，仍有不同的際遇，中韓兩國經濟情勢最好，美日港大致平平，新加坡則在谷底中奮鬥。"},{"pid":"5a1db79fd5e9ee4d3fba781b97f133eeb65927e2","tid":1050677,"uid":14758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"新加坡則在谷底中奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}